<h1 class='property-title'>border-width</h1>
<p class='property-description'>The<code> border-width </code>CSS property sets the width of the border of a box. Using the shorthand property <code><a rel="custom" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS/border">border</a></code>
